<h2 id="org500bc7a">What is an algorithm?</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org500bc7a">
<p>
And algorithm is the idea/ solution to a problem in computer science.
</p>

<p>
We strive to create correct awnser on every single input.
We measure efficient with <a href="20230305150253-big_o.html#ID-a6dfee7d-c44e-4cbf-93c2-3461b91158f5">big o</a> notation.
</p>
